name: Super Space-Stronaut (Alexgabbard86)
description:
This is my complete submission for the 2D Platformer project.

My modifications:

1. All 10 levels individually designed as complete interesting, comprehensive, and coherent levels.

2. Seven additional levels including a boss level at the end.

3. My own custom music was added to the main menu and for the levels.

Created by Alex Gabbard

Music was made using Music Maker Steam Edition.
